      "instruction": "Add the olive oil to your electric pressure cooker insert. Using the saut\u00e9/brown function, heat the oil and cook the onions, garlic, and jalape\u00f1o for 3-4 minutes. Add the cumin and oregano and saut\u00e9 for another minute or two."
